Installation
============
It is recommanded to use Debian Lenny or above

python-django (>1.0) python-sqlalchemy python-psycopg2 postgresql libapache2-mod-auth-psql

django 1.0 packaged for debian is available on http://nirgal.com

Apache
======
Enable ssl and auth_pgsql in apache:
a2enmod ssl 000_auth_pgsql

Generate self-signed certificate:
openssl req -nodes -x509 -days 3650 -new -newkey rsa:2048 -subj /CN=nike.fr.gl3 -keyout nike.key -out nike.crt

Listen on port 443
Add a new line "Listen 443" to /etc/apache2/ports.conf"

Thougths
========

Create a root group for all contacts?
=> No more users page, see /contactgroups/gid/members
=> No more fields page, see /contactgroups/gid/contactfields
=> Operator of group 1 / Can add / Can delete ... / Can see list

